---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Fishing Net — Wenji Makes" description="A craftable fishing net for Stardew Valley that catches fish overnight.">
  <div class="mod-header"><div class="container">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;"><span class="tag">Tool</span><span class="tag">Fishing</span><span class="tag">Automation</span></div>
    <h1>Fishing Net</h1><p class="meta">1.0.0 · SMAPI 4.0+ · Mod ID: 47586</p>
  </div></div>
  <section class="mod-content container">
    <img src="https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/1303/images/headers/47586_1781331053.jpg" alt="Fishing Net" class="mod-image-full" />
    <p><strong>Add a craftable fishing net, place it in the water overnight, and collect fish the next day.</strong></p>
    <p>This mod adds a more passive fishing rhythm without making it completely effortless. Nets lose durability over time, so you still need to check, maintain, and replace them.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-muted);margin:12px 0 24px 20px;">
      <li>Craftable fishing nets</li><li>Place them on suitable water tiles</li><li>Catch fish overnight</li><li>Durability and upkeep</li><li>Designed to complement, not replace, normal fishing</li>
    </ul>
    <div style="margin-top:40px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;"><a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/47586" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Download on Nexus Mods</a><a href="/en/mods" class="btn btn-outline">← Back to Mods</a></div>
  </section>
</Layout>
